<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFJohnson1981" class="citation cs2">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212; (1981), Davis, William (ed.), <i>The Best of Everything – Animals, Business, Drink, Travel, Food, Literature, Medicine, Playtime, Politics, Theatre, Young World, Art, Communications, Law and Crime, Films, Pop Culture, Sport, Women's Fashion, Men's Fashion, Music, Military</i></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Best+of+Everything+%E2%80%93+Animals%2C+Business%2C+Drink%2C+Travel%2C+Food%2C+Literature%2C+Medicine%2C+Playtime%2C+Politics%2C+Theatre%2C+Young+World%2C+Art%2C+Communications%2C+Law+and+Crime%2C+Films%2C+Pop+Culture%2C+Sport%2C+Women%27s+Fashion%2C+Men%27s+Fashion%2C+Music%2C+Military&amp;rft.date=1981&amp;rft.aulast=Johnson&amp;rft.aufirst=Paul+Bede&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APaul+Johnson+%28writer%29" class="Z3988"></span> – contributor.</li>
